author: dallasnews
title: Dave Eggers headed to Highland Park
text:
Dave Eggers, one of the most dynamic literary forces in America, is coming to Highland Park for their literary festival.
Eggers is best known for A Heartbreaking Work of Staggering Genius . He’s also founder of McSweeney’s, which publishes top-notch books and the literary journal McSweeney’s Quarterly Concern and The Believer magazine. He also launched what became 826 National, a network of creative writing and tutoring centers.
The public can see him at a free event 7 p.m. Feb. 25 at Highland Park High School. Details are posted at hplitfest.com .
Michael Merschel
